data.title: Seaside shambles
data.meta_description: Law suits, money shortages and strong-arm tactics have dogged the sea baths development in Melbourne
data.text:
Law suits, money shortages and strong-arm tactics have dogged the sea baths development in Melbourne

On the evening of April 21 this year, after nearly a decade of controversy and bitter legal battles, there was a mood of celebration at the sea baths on the St Kilda foreshore
